[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0714","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0714.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0459","title":"Linux Alpha MILO 本地拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Alpha Linux 系统中存在本地拒绝服务漏洞。本地攻击者可通过 MILO 引导加载程序强制系统重新启动，导致系统服务不可用。该漏洞影响运行 Alpha Linux 的 DEC Alpha 架构系统，攻击者需具备本地访问权限，无需高权限即可利用，CVSS 评分 4.6，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0459"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-02-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:26.440","remediation":"建议升级 MILO 引导程序至最新版本，并限制系统本地用户的登录访问权限。在生产环境中应禁用不必要的本地用户账号，并通过 `/etc/security/access.conf` 或 PAM 模块限制控制台访问。对于 Alpha 架构系统，可考虑迁移至更新的 Linux 内核版本以规避该引导层问题。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0459"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0714.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0613","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0613.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0373","title":"Debian GNU/Linux Super 缓冲区溢出本地权限提升漏洞","description":"Debian GNU/Linux 及多个类 Unix 系统中自带的 Super 工具存在栈缓冲区溢出漏洞。该程序以 setuid root 权限运行，用于授权普通用户以 root 身份执行特定命令。攻击者通过向 Super 提交超长的命令行参数触发缓冲区溢出，可覆盖返回地址并劫持控制流，从而以 root 权限执行任意代码。由于攻击者需要本地系统访问权限，该漏洞影响范围局限于多用户环境，但一旦利用成功即实现完全提权。CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0373"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-02-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:15.430","remediation":"升级 Debian GNU/Linux 上的 super 软件包至版本 3.12 及以上，该版本已修复缓冲区溢出问题。如无法升级，立即执行 `chmod u-s /usr/bin/super` 移除 suid 权限位以阻止提权利用，并考虑使用 sudo 替代 super 进行权限委派。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0373"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0613.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0590","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0590.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0358","title":"Digital Unix 4.0 MH inc 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Digital Unix 4.0 操作系统的 mh（消息处理）套件中的 inc 程序存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。本地或远程攻击者可通过向目标系统发送特制的邮件消息触发该漏洞，导致缓冲区溢出，进而造成程序崩溃或执行任意代码，获取系统控制权限。该漏洞影响 Digital Unix 4.0 版本，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0358"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-02-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:13.480","remediation":"立即从 Compaq（现 HP）获取并安装 Digital Unix 4.0 的安全补丁（补丁编号请查阅 CIAC 公告 J-027），或升级至 Tru64 UNIX 5.0 及以上版本。若无法立即打补丁，可移除 inc 程序的 setuid 位（chmod u-s /usr/bin/inc）作为临时缓解措施，限制本地普通用户以 root 权限执行 inc 命令。建议改用 mailx 或 Mutt 替代 mh 套件处理本地邮件，降低攻击面。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.ciac.org/ciac/bulletins/j-027.shtml","http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/12121"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0590.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0583","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0583.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0351","title":"多厂商 FTP 服务器 PASV 模式拒绝服务与未授权数据访问漏洞","description":"FTP 协议 PASV 被动模式存在设计缺陷，远程攻击者可利用竞争条件在合法客户端之前连接至服务器为该客户端开放的临时数据端口，导致未经授权的数据访问和敏感信息窃取。若攻击者抢先占用该数据端口，还可导致合法客户端无法完成数据传输，造成拒绝服务。该漏洞影响多种 FTP 服务器实现，攻击者无需认证即可远程利用，CVSS 评分 6.4，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":6.4,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0351"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-02-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:12.610","remediation":"升级至支持 PASV 地址绑定检查的 FTP 服务器（如 vsftpd 3.0+、ProFTPD 1.3.5+），配置数据端口仅接受与控制连接相同 IP 的连接请求。启用 FTPS（FTP over TLS/SSL，RFC 2228）加密数据通道防止窃听；条件允许时切换到 SFTP/SCP。在服务器上限制 PASV 端口范围为固定区间，并通过防火墙仅允许预期客户端 IP 访问该端口段作为临时缓解。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://attrition.org/security/advisory/misc/infowar/iw_sec_01.txt","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/3389","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ead50dc12e50bdd7f50b53d9d01c9f9946862c44/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0351.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0351","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0351.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/4ed191c1149de50e461e9a357f4a3a22e603f0d1/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0351.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/b7a93df7f7051799495805bc211adea8d202dae7/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-8xwf-5pv7-g2w4/GHSA-8xwf-5pv7-g2w4.json","https://github.com/CWE-CAPEC/REST-API-wg/blob/5a8974308ef38e8ee4979e4a29b3b3a22c647822/json_repo/W/421.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x83000/82479/info.html","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0351.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cwe_details/cwe_details_100_200.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000509.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0583.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0485","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0485.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0291","title":"Qbik WinGate 代理默认无密码未授权访问漏洞","description":"WinGate 代理服务器在默认安装时未设置访问密码，导致缺乏必要的身份认证机制。远程攻击者可在无需任何认证的条件下连接至该代理服务，利用其开放的代理功能转发网络连接请求，从而隐藏攻击来源、绕过访问控制或发起匿名攻击。该漏洞影响 WinGate 全系列早期版本，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0291"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-02-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:05.093","remediation":"立即为 WinGate 代理服务设置管理密码并启用用户认证机制；在 GateKeeper 管理控制台中配置访问控制列表，仅允许受信任的内部 IP 地址段使用代理服务；如业务不需要代理功能，直接卸载或禁用 WinGate 服务；同时在网络防火墙层面拦截外部对 8080/1080 等常见代理端口的入站连接作为临时缓解。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0291","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-0291.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/1421f0a4349d5d46275cadd9c7c62349edf9c8bb/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0291.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0291","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0291.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/db45dbc75ff0264d63b603291e4a83d7361bd7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0291.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0291.md","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0291.json","https://github.com/Freem93/grammar_nasl_v2/blob/63834ebb8cd6e97050e155291c7500ad53bb20c6/plugins/wingate.nasl","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0485.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0644","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0644.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0403","title":"Cyrix CPU Linux 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Cyrix CPU 在 Linux 系统中存在硬件设计缺陷，本地攻击者可通过执行特定指令序列触发处理器异常，导致系统崩溃或拒绝服务。该漏洞影响使用 Cyrix 处理器的 Linux 系统，攻击者需拥有本地用户权限才能利用，无法远程触发。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0403"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-02-01","updated":"1999-02-01","remediation":"更换非 Cyrix 品牌的处理器，或升级 Linux 内核至包含 Cyrix CPU 异常处理补丁的版本。由于该漏洞为硬件设计缺陷，最彻底的修复方式是更换为 Intel 或 AMD 等主流处理器。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=91821080015725&w=2"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0644.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0591","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0591.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0360","title":"Microsoft Site Server 2.0 任意文件上传漏洞","description":"Microsoft Site Server 2.0 与 IIS 4.0 存在任意文件上传漏洞，远程攻击者可通过 HTTP 协议向目标网站上传包含 ASP 脚本的恶意文件，从而在服务器端执行任意命令。该漏洞影响 Microsoft Site Server 2.0 及 IIS 4.0 版本，攻击者无需身份认证即可利用，危害等级高。厂商已发布安全更新修复此漏洞。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0360"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-01-30","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"安装 Microsoft 官方针对 Site Server 2.0 的安全更新补丁，或禁用 IIS 4.0 中 Site Server 上传目录的脚本执行权限（移除 Scripts 和 Execute 权限），限制匿名用户对上传目录的写入权限。由于该产品已停止支持，建议迁移至受支持的替代产品。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=91763097004101&w=2"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0591.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1235","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1235.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0952","title":"Sun Solaris lpstat 命令类参数缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Solaris 系统的 lpstat 命令在处理 class 参数时存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。本地未授权用户可通过向 lpstat 传入超长的 class 参数触发溢出，进而以 root 权限执行任意代码。该漏洞影响 Solaris 2.6 和 SunOS 5.7 等多个版本，攻击者需具备本地登录权限或可执行 lpstat 命令的访问权，利用后可完全控制系统。建议及时应用 Solaris 官方安全补丁并限制非授权用户对 lpstat 命令的访问权限。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0952"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-28T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:23.740","remediation":"应用 Sun 官方安全补丁或升级到 Solaris 8 及以上版本，并通过 chmod 移除普通用户对 lpstat 命令的可执行权限。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=91759216618637&w=2","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/f54846af4ec1affce3d519a6791531e8f1f5b8fe/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0952.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0952","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/e046e4965f64348bd29a0c62edd023b3c580939e/content/CVE-1999-0952.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/cf6074d8ac2128dee0a2ac26c5f652ae6527df79/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0952.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/8b1565557a8e0fb04634f0989d7e7dd7febd4847/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-7qmh-2c8x-qh3g/GHSA-7qmh-2c8x-qh3g.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0952.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153200_153300.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--4776cb8a-247a-4733-b1bf-b02b6f76eec1.json","https://github.com/hungryfoolou/Vulnerability_Mining/blob/3df1d8ed0489ae1228f975ae1f58a690aae53886/craw/cveid_craw/cveid_craw/data/cveid_by_kind/cveid_overflow.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/233cd9746ce3c3e9d47fe0335940ddf03b9a0845/1999.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1235.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0717","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0717.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0461","title":"Linux rpcbind 远程源地址欺骗漏洞","description":"rpcbind（端口映射服务）存在认证缺陷漏洞，远程攻击者可通过伪造源地址向目标系统的 rpcbind 服务发送恶意请求，从而插入或删除 RPC 服务注册条目，破坏服务映射表或劫持 RPC 服务通信。该漏洞影响 Linux、IRIX 及 Wietse Venema 实现的 rpcbind 等多个版本，攻击者无需身份认证即可远程利用，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0461"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-01-28","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"升级 rpcbind 至已修复版本以解决源地址欺骗漏洞。在防火墙层面限制对 UDP/TCP 111 端口的访问，仅允许可信来源 IP 连接。配置 TCP Wrappers（/etc/hosts.allow 和 /etc/hosts.deny）限制 rpcbind 的访问来源。如非必要，可在服务配置中禁用 rpcbind 服务。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0461","https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-1999-0461"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0717.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0573","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0573.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0349","title":"Microsoft IIS FTP LIST 命令缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Microsoft IIS 的 FTP 服务中的 list (ls) 命令存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可向目标服务器发送特制的 FTP 列表请求触发该漏洞，导致拒绝服务或远程代码执行。该漏洞影响早期版本的 IIS，攻击条件低，危害严重，建议及时安装安全补丁。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0349"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-01-27T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:12.357","remediation":"建议立即安装 Microsoft 安全公告 MS99-003 提供的补丁（Q223783），或升级至 IIS 5.0 及以上版本。如无法升级，可在 IIS 管理器中禁用 FTP 服务（停止 MSFTPSVC 服务），或限制匿名用户对 FTP 根目录的写入权限以降低风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/default.aspx?scid=kb%3B%5BLN%5D%3BQ188348","http://www.eeye.com/html/Research/Advisories/IIS%20Remote%20FTP%20Exploit/DoS%20Attack.html","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-003","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ead50dc12e50bdd7f50b53d9d01c9f9946862c44/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0349.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0349","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0349.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/4ed191c1149de50e461e9a357f4a3a22e603f0d1/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0349.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/b7a93df7f7051799495805bc211adea8d202dae7/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-hcx3-7fvg-jr7j/GHSA-hcx3-7fvg-jr7j.json","https://github.com/marcellodesales/aibbp-reverse-engineer/blob/960f610d597aae9fec1cc5f03c68679be00c222d/reverse_engineer/invicti/vulnerabilities/db/vulnerabilities/vdb/1999/0xxx/cve-1999-0349.yaml","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/I/iis_ftp_crash.nasl","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0349.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153100_153200.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0573.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0571","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0571.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0348","title":"Microsoft IIS ASP 缓存信息泄露漏洞","description":"Microsoft Internet Information Server (IIS) 的 ASP 缓存机制存在信息泄露漏洞。当两个虚拟服务器共享同一物理目录时，ASP 脚本缓存未能正确隔离不同虚拟服务器之间的数据，导致攻击者可通过向目标服务器发送特制请求，获取同一物理目录下其他虚拟站点的敏感信息。该漏洞影响多个 IIS 版本，公开利用难度较低，可能导致网站配置文件、源代码等敏感数据泄露，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0348"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-01-27T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:12.237","remediation":"建议立即安装 Microsoft KB Q197003 安全更新（包含于 Windows NT 4.0 Security Rollup Package），该更新修复了 ASP 脚本缓存在虚拟服务器间的隔离问题。如无法安装补丁，应将每个虚拟服务器配置为使用独立的物理目录，避免不同虚拟主机共用同一目录；也可在 IIS 管理控制台中禁用 ASP 脚本文件缓存作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/default.aspx?scid=kb%3B%5BLN%5D%3BQ197003","http://www.osvdb.org/930","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ead50dc12e50bdd7f50b53d9d01c9f9946862c44/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0348.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0348","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0348.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/4ed191c1149de50e461e9a357f4a3a22e603f0d1/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0348.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/b7a93df7f7051799495805bc211adea8d202dae7/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-q6hg-qxrw-r3f8/GHSA-q6hg-qxrw-r3f8.json","https://github.com/marcellodesales/aibbp-reverse-engineer/blob/960f610d597aae9fec1cc5f03c68679be00c222d/reverse_engineer/invicti/vulnerabilities/db/vulnerabilities/vdb/1999/0xxx/cve-1999-0348.yaml","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0348.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153100_153200.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0571.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0685","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0685.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0449","title":"Microsoft IIS 4 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Microsoft IIS 4.0 的 ExAir 示例站点中存在拒绝服务漏洞。远程攻击者无需身份认证，通过直接向 advsearch.asp、query.asp 或 search.asp 脚本发送特制请求，即可触发 CPU 资源耗尽，导致目标系统拒绝服务。该漏洞影响运行 IIS 4.0 的 Windows NT 4.0 系统，攻击条件低，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.8,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0449"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-01-26T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:25.213","remediation":"升级到 Windows 2000 及以上版本自带的 IIS 5.0 或更高版本，或直接移除 IIS 4 默认安装的 ExAir 示例站点目录（通常位于 C:\\InetPub\\iissamples\\exair），删除 advsearch.asp、query.asp、search.asp 等脚本文件。如无法升级，可在 IIS 管理器中禁用该示例站点的匿名访问权限作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/2","http://www.osvdb.org/3","http://www.osvdb.org/4","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/193","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/6e5939e8074723d33adaf5b2f8b0352edab9ba8d/1999/CVE-1999-0449.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/727cf5277c8c23eaf8725829e26aff2ea619a86c/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0449.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0449","https://github.com/edoardottt/missing-cve-nuclei-templates/blob/36c16d53eb6071e39cfc3cf88e99f1b340ec913b/data/year/1999.txt","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/77fd3cf167afc5c82646a191836bcd2f9e51b459/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0449.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0449.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/18de81c56daca1c9e33223f0b95bdb8312a1ca75/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-9mvc-88j3-6fmc/GHSA-9mvc-88j3-6fmc.json","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/snort/drop-rules/web-iis.rules","https://github.com/marcellodesales/aibbp-reverse-engineer/blob/960f610d597aae9fec1cc5f03c68679be00c222d/reverse_engineer/invicti/vulnerabilities/db/vulnerabilities/vdb/1999/0xxx/cve-1999-0449.yaml","https://github.com/ivanitlearning/CTF-Repos/blob/b5364388a861fc7457409d494a9d075d73e7867e/Vulnhub/SkyTower/Web-scan.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0685.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0640","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0640.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0400","title":"Linux Kernel 2.2 ldd命令处理core文件拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Linux Kernel 2.2 版本的 ldd 命令在处理恶意构造的 core 文件时存在拒绝服务漏洞。本地攻击者可通过诱导用户在包含畸形数据的 core 文件上执行 ldd 命令，触发内核异常导致系统强制重启。该漏洞影响 Linux Kernel 2.2.0 及之前版本，CVSS 评分 4.6，危害等级中危。受影响的系统在攻击者获得普通用户权限后即可实施该攻击，无需额外认证。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0400"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1999-01-26T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:19.000","remediation":"升级 Linux 内核至 2.2.1 或更高版本，该版本已修复 ldd 解析 core 文件时的崩溃问题。如无法立即升级，作为临时缓解措施，禁止对不可信的 core 文件运行 ldd 命令，并通过 sysctl -w kernel.core_uses_pid=1 和设置 fs.suid_dumpable=0 限制核心转储文件的生成与访问权限。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/344","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19272","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/f4ffb7bcd93209aa53a757a7ebdf17fe2a18eb33/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0400.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0400","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0400.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a75ebb477762f54f32c38d85ec939339ec2712e5/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0400.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/e434c1da6464de3012c6c1eff8c0e19ef9669023/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-2x32-727m-44f2/GHSA-2x32-727m-44f2.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0400.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x1000/344/info.html","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_3.list.dict","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--e45afe65-1461-434d-a73e-c70299fe4ea0.json","https://github.com/shamedgh/confine/blob/a75dad3ad336e6258a42cd1ce4af061eea68ed76/cve.files/cveToFile.json.type.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0640.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0688","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0688.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0450","title":"Microsoft IIS 5.0 IISAPI扩展目录枚举漏洞","description":"Microsoft IIS 5.0 存在路径信息泄露漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向服务器发送特制的非存在 URL 请求（由 Perl 解释器 perl.exe 处理），从而枚举出 Web 服务器的真实物理路径。该漏洞影响 IIS 5.0 版本，攻击者无需身份认证即可利用，可能导致敏感系统路径信息泄露，为进一步攻击提供线索。CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0450"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-01-26","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"升级到受支持的 Windows Server 版本（IIS 5.0 已停止支持），或迁移至 IIS 7.0 及以上版本。如无法升级，在 IIS 管理器中删除 Perl ISAPI 扩展映射（perl.exe），并配置自定义错误页面禁止返回详细路径信息，同时限制 IIS 对非可执行目录的脚本映射权限。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/194","https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-1999-0450"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0688.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0688.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0688.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0569","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0569.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0347","title":"Microsoft Internet Explorer 跨框架访问安全限制绕过漏洞","description":"Microsoft Internet Explorer 4.01 及 5.0.1 版本存在跨帧访问安全漏洞。远程攻击者可通过在 'about:' JavaScript URL 中插入 '%01' 特殊字符，诱使浏览器使用该字符后指定的域名解析页面，从而绕过同源策略限制，实现跨域读取本地文件内容或伪造任意网页。攻击者需诱导用户访问恶意构造的链接即可触发，无需任何身份认证，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0347"],"sources":["cve","exploitdb"],"published":"1999-01-26","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"升级到 Internet Explorer 5.5 及以上版本即可修复此漏洞。由于 Internet Explorer 已停止安全支持，强烈建议迁移到 Microsoft Edge 或其他现代浏览器（如 Chrome/Firefox），并启用 Windows 自动更新以保持系统安全。如无法升级浏览器，可在 IE 安全设置中将 Internet 区域安全级别设为高并禁用活动脚本。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=91745430007021&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=ntbugtraq&m=91756771207719&w=2"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0569.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0569.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0569.toml"}]